Class OnlineXmlDataStore

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.uadetector.datastore.AbstractRefreshableDataStore
      net.sf.uadetector.json.OnlineXmlDataStore
All Implemented Interfaces:
net.sf.uadetector.datastore.DataStore, net.sf.uadetector.datastore.RefreshableDataStore
public class OnlineXmlDataStore
extends net.sf.uadetector.datastore.AbstractRefreshableDataStore

This is a very simple implementation of a DataStore for test cases. It initialize the store by reading the UAS data via test URLs and store it only in the Java heap space.

Author:
André Rouél
